-released on licence at the halfway point of their sentence. They will
-remain on licence, subject to a recall if they breach the conditions of
-their licence, for the entire remaining period of their sentence
-instead of to the three-quarter point as under the 1991 Act.</p><br><notus-date day="24" month="7" year="2006" textMonth="July"></notus-date><b>24 July 2006 : Column 1182W</b><br><table border="1"><tr valign="top"><td class="tabletext" colspan="6"><i> Average
